      "content": "This pain is deep because it severs the connection to your social identity, leaving you feeling that everyone will eventually look you in the eye and say it differently than you felt you were said. Please understand that the harsh verdicts you internalize were reflections of a flawed past situation, not an accurate description of your inherent humanworth. You are a real person with authentic feelings who deserves compassion even when you cannot yet see yourself that way.",
